timing_report_enable_si_debug(25.10)      timing_report_enable_si_debug(25.10)

Name
       timing_report_enable_si_debug

Syntax
       timing_report_enable_si_debug

       {true | false}

       Default: false

       Allows  the  software  to capture signal integrity (SI) related details
       for each stage of a path being analyzed during path-based  analysis  in
       the form of attributes.

       To set this global variable, use the set command.

